show_name: Chō Tanpen PreCure All Stars GoGo Dream Live! (movie)
other_title: ちょ～短編 プリキュアオールスターズ GoGoドリームライブ！ (Japanese)
plot: The PreCure teams from Max Heart, Splash Star and Yes 5 GoGo visit a big live performance. When they get there they find the arena taken over by a dark giant. They all fight it together so that the show can continue.
ending_theme: "DANZEN! Makasete☆Full Throttle GoGo!!" by Mayumi Gojo, Yuka Uchiyae, Mayu Kudou
